  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Currently both Beaconnode and Validator client push 1 update each every minute. That sums up to 89.280 calls per month (31 days * 24 hrs * 60 minutes * 2 calls per minute) while the Beaconcha.in Free Tier API calls are limited to 30.000 calls per month. Most Solo stakers won't be willing to spend 59USD per month to upgrade to a paid Tier API level. Is there a possibility to customize the update frequency or put the default to 3 minutes? \r\nI do believe this issue affects all clients as this spec here: https://github.com/gobitfly/eth2-client-metrics from Buttaa specifies 1 update every minute.",
